author: Giorgio Mendoza
description: IBASE Technology has introduced the IBR500, a 3.5-inch single board computer built around MediaTek Genio processors. The compact design is aimed at embedded and edge applications that prioritize low power consumption and efficient use of space. The board integrates the MediaTek Genio 700 (MT8390) at up to 2.2 GHz or the Genio 510 (MT8370) at […]
title: 3.5” SBC with MediaTek Genio 700/510 for Low-Power AIoT Edge Applications
